{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.1","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:1","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.033.033,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Contre les chefs d\u2019Isra\u00ebl<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-10: cf. J\u00e9 23:1-3. Za 11:15-17. Ac 20:28.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel me fut adress\u00e9e, en ces mots:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.2","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.33.33","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 33:33","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.33.33"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.2","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:2","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Fils de l\u2019homme, proph\u00e9tise contre les pasteurs d\u2019Isra\u00ebl! Proph\u00e9tise, et dis-leur, aux pasteurs: Ainsi parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Malheur aux pasteurs d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, qui se paissaient eux-m\u00eames! Les pasteurs ne devaient-ils pas pa\u00eetre le troupeau?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.3","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.1","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.3","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:3","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Vous avez mang\u00e9 la graisse, vous vous \u00eates v\u00eatus avec la laine, vous avez tu\u00e9 ce qui \u00e9tait gras, vous n\u2019avez point fait pa\u00eetre les brebis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.4","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.2","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.4","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:4","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Vous n\u2019avez pas fortifi\u00e9 celles qui \u00e9taient faibles, gu\u00e9ri celle qui \u00e9tait malade, pans\u00e9 celle qui \u00e9tait bless\u00e9e; vous n\u2019avez pas ramen\u00e9 celle qui s\u2019\u00e9garait, cherch\u00e9 celle qui \u00e9tait perdue; mais vous les avez domin\u00e9es avec violence et avec duret\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.5","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.3","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.5","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:5","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Elles se sont dispers\u00e9es, parce qu\u2019elles n\u2019avaient point de pasteur; elles sont devenues la proie de toutes les b\u00eates des champs, elles se sont dispers\u00e9es.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.6","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.4","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.6","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:6","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>Mon troupeau est errant sur toutes les montagnes et sur toutes les collines \u00e9lev\u00e9es, mon troupeau est dispers\u00e9 sur toute la face du pays; nul n\u2019en prend souci, nul ne le cherche.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.7","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.5","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.7","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:7","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi, pasteurs, \u00e9coutez la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.8","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.6","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.8","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:8","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Je suis vivant! Dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, parce que mes brebis sont au pillage et qu\u2019elles sont devenues la proie de toutes les b\u00eates des champs, faute de pasteur, parce que mes pasteurs ne prenaient aucun souci de mes brebis, qu\u2019ils se paissaient eux-m\u00eames, et ne faisaient point pa\u00eetre mes brebis,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.9","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.7","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.9","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:9","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>\u00e0 cause de cela, pasteurs, \u00e9coutez la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.10","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.8","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.10","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:10","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Ainsi parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Voici, j\u2019en veux aux pasteurs! Je reprendrai mes brebis d\u2019entre leurs mains, je ne les laisserai plus pa\u00eetre mes brebis, et ils ne se pa\u00eetront plus eux-m\u00eames; je d\u00e9livrerai mes brebis de leur bouche, et elles ne seront plus pour eux une proie.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.11","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.9","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.11","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:11","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.012,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">Promesses au peuple<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 11-19: cf. J\u00e9 23:3, 4, 7, 8; 30:16-20. Mi 7:12-15.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Car ainsi parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Voici, j\u2019aurai soin moi-m\u00eame de mes brebis, et j\u2019en ferai la revue.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.12","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.10","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.12","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:12","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Comme un pasteur inspecte son troupeau quand il est au milieu de ses brebis \u00e9parses, ainsi je ferai la revue de mes brebis, et je les recueillerai de tous les lieux o\u00f9 elles ont \u00e9t\u00e9 dispers\u00e9es au jour des nuages et de l\u2019obscurit\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.13","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.11","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.13","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:13","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Je les retirerai d\u2019entre les peuples, je les rassemblerai des diverses contr\u00e9es, et je les ram\u00e8nerai dans leur pays; je les ferai pa\u00eetre sur les montagnes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, le long des ruisseaux, et dans tous les lieux habit\u00e9s du pays.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.14","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.12","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.14","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:14","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Je les ferai pa\u00eetre dans un bon p\u00e2turage, et leur demeure sera sur les montagnes \u00e9lev\u00e9es d\u2019Isra\u00ebl; l\u00e0 elles reposeront dans un agr\u00e9able asile, et elles auront de gras p\u00e2turages sur les montagnes d\u2019Isra\u00ebl.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.15","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.13","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.15","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:15","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.016,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>C\u2019est moi qui ferai pa\u00eetre mes brebis, c\u2019est moi qui les ferai reposer, dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.16","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.14","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.16","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:16","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Je chercherai celle qui \u00e9tait perdue, je ram\u00e8nerai celle qui \u00e9tait \u00e9gar\u00e9e, je panserai celle qui est bless\u00e9e, et je fortifierai celle qui est malade. Mais je d\u00e9truirai celles qui sont grasses et vigoureuses. Je veux les pa\u00eetre avec justice.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.17","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.15","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.17","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:17","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Et vous, mes brebis, ainsi parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Voici, je jugerai entre brebis et brebis, entre b\u00e9liers et boucs.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.16","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.18","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:18","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>Est-ce trop peu pour vous de pa\u00eetre dans le bon p\u00e2turage, pour que vous fouliez de vos pieds le reste de votre p\u00e2turage? De boire une eau limpide, pour que vous troubliez le reste avec vos pieds?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.19","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.17","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.19","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:19","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Et mes brebis doivent pa\u00eetre ce que vos pieds ont foul\u00e9, et boire ce que vos pieds ont troubl\u00e9!<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.20","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.20","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:20","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.021,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 20-31: cf. J\u00e9 23:4-6. \u00c9z 37:22-28.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi ainsi leur parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Voici, je jugerai entre la brebis grasse et la brebis maigre.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.21","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.19","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.21","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:21","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Parce que vous avez heurt\u00e9 avec le c\u00f4t\u00e9 et avec l\u2019\u00e9paule, et frapp\u00e9 de vos cornes toutes les brebis faibles, jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que vous les ayez chass\u00e9es,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.22","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.20","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.22","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:22","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>je porterai secours \u00e0 mes brebis, afin qu\u2019elles ne soient plus au pillage, et je jugerai entre brebis et brebis.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.23","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.21","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.23","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:23","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>J\u2019\u00e9tablirai sur elles un seul pasteur, qui les fera pa\u00eetre, mon serviteur David; il les fera pa\u00eetre, il sera leur pasteur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.22","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.24","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:24","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Moi, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, je serai leur Dieu, et mon serviteur David sera prince au milieu d\u2019elles. Moi, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, j\u2019ai parl\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.25","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.23","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.25","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:25","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Je traiterai avec elles une alliance de paix, et je ferai dispara\u00eetre du pays les animaux sauvages; elles habiteront en s\u00e9curit\u00e9 dans le d\u00e9sert, et dormiront au milieu des for\u00eats.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.26","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.26","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:26","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>Je ferai d\u2019elles et des environs de ma colline un sujet de b\u00e9n\u00e9diction; j\u2019enverrai la pluie en son temps, et ce sera une pluie de b\u00e9n\u00e9diction.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.27","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.25","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.27","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:27","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.028,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>L\u2019arbre des champs donnera son fruit, et la terre donnera ses produits. Elles seront en s\u00e9curit\u00e9 dans leur pays; et elles sauront que je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel, quand je briserai les liens de leur joug, et que je les d\u00e9livrerai de la main de ceux qui les asservissaient.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.28","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:28","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.28"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.26","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"28","lastverse":"28","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.28","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.28","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:28","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.027,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.029,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.28\" class=\"v\">28<\/sup>Elles ne seront plus au pillage parmi les nations, les b\u00eates de la terre ne les d\u00e9voreront plus, elles habiteront en s\u00e9curit\u00e9, et il n\u2019y aura personne pour les troubler.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.29","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:29","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.29"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.27","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.27"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"29","lastverse":"29","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.29","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.29","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:29","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.028,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.030,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.29\" class=\"v\">29<\/sup>J\u2019\u00e9tablirai pour elles une plantation qui aura du renom; elles ne seront plus consum\u00e9es par la faim dans le pays, et elles ne porteront plus l\u2019opprobre des nations.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.30","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:30","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.30"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.28","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:28","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.28"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"30","lastverse":"30","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.30","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.30","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:30","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.029,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.034.031,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.30\" class=\"v\">30<\/sup>Et elles sauront que moi, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, leur Dieu, je suis avec elles, et qu\u2019elles sont mon peuple, elles, la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl, dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.31","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:31","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.31"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.29","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:29","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.29"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"31","lastverse":"31","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.31","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.31","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:31","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.034.030,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.035.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.34.31\" class=\"v\">31<\/sup>Vous, mes brebis, brebis de mon p\u00e2turage, vous \u00eates des hommes; moi, je suis votre Dieu, dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.35.1","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 35:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.35.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.34.30","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 34:30","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.34.30"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fbd83a7a2.69774912');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fbd83a7a2.69774912\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fbd83a7a2.69774912","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fbd83a7a2.69774912'); }","fums_n